T declaration header candidate
^\s*//\s*#threshold\s+

T declaration header
^\s*//\s*#threshold\s+"[^:"]+"\s*$

T declaration body
^\s*const\s+int\s+[a-zA-Z_][a-zA-Z0-9_]*\s*=\s*(0|([1-9][0-9]*))*\s*;\s*$

T declarations end tag
^\s*//\s*#threshold-declarations-end\s*$

T configuration entry
^[^:\"]+:\s+(0|([1-9][0-9]*))\s*$
